Package: E.PAGE
Type: Package
Title: Environmental Pathways Affecting Gene Expression
Version: 1.2.0
Authors@R:
    c(person("Lilin", "Yang", role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "lilin.yang@uq.net.au"),
      person("Ahmed", "Mehdi", role = "ctb",
             email = "a.mehdi@imb.uq.edu.au"))
Description: A package containing a curated database and enrichment tool to
    predict modules associated with gene-environment interactions. This package
    can also extract differentially-expressed genes from Seurat objects and
    visually display enriched pathways.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
